        "description": "<p>With the use of the <a href=\"http://sunlightfoundation.com/api/accounts/register/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Sunlight API</a>, this widget will show the most recently updated information regarding spending by Political Action Committees (PACs).</p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>Independent Donations Widget</code> to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>Use the &#8216;Independent Donations Widget&#8217; option in the Appearance-&gt;Widgets area and install in a widget area.</li>\n<li>Insert the Sunlight API Key in the widget options</li>\n<li>Enjoy!</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<h4>Will the Widget update in real-time?</h4>\n<p>The widget is not currently setup for that option. In the future, there should be an update the allows for this feature.</p>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First release! &#8211; 22md December, 2014*</li>\n</ul>\n"
